The tesng-webtest-quickstart project is a sample project that can be used to quickly get started writing Selenium test cases
in TestNG.  It includes samples for running tests locally and remotely, and sample maven profiles for driving tests
using different browser types and combinations.



For additional details regarding the testng-webdriver, the library that provides the WebDriverBase used by the tests:
https://github.com/dev9com/test-webdrivers